column8: Partly cloudy. Winds northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light in the early afternoon.
Partly cloudy. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Light winds.
Partly cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h.
Cloudy. Very high (near 100%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon. Winds northwesterly 30 to 40 km/h shifting southerly 20 to 25 km/h during the afternoon.
Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 25 to 30 km/h tending southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers. Winds southeasterly 20 to 25 km/h.
Partly cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely later in the day. Winds east to southeasterly 20 to 25 km/h shifting north to northwesterly during the day.
